  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bb0\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0bae\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0bb3\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb3\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Political parties should act in such a way as to gain people's trust - Tri-Army Commanders demand",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Political party leaders should hold talks with the protestors and urge them to be patient till the coming 20th. The commanders of the three forces and the Inspector General of Police urged the leaders of the political parties to act in such a way that the people of the country believe that the political and economic crisis will be resolved through the Parliament.",
        "A special party leader meeting was held yesterday evening under the chairmanship of the Speaker to discuss the next steps to be taken regarding the current situation in the country.",
        "The party leaders gathered before the start of the party leader's meeting continued to insist that acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe should step down immediately.",
        "Chief of Defense Forces General Shavendra Silva spoke about the current security situation in the country. The current situation can be controlled by the security forces The security forces have controlled the situation using minimum power, the security forces said.",
        "Instruct the political party leaders to negotiate with the protestors and act with patience on the 20th.",
        "The commanders of the three forces urged the leaders of the political parties to give hope to the people of the country that all the problems can be resolved through the government established through the Parliament.",
        "We cannot do that. Ranil Wickremesinghe should step down as Acting President. Party leaders have mentioned that no problem can be solved by keeping him in office.",
        "It was insisted in the party leader's meeting that Acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe should step down before President Gotabaya Rajapakse's letter of resignation is officially handed over to Sabanayan.",
        "Party leaders Maithripala Sirisena, Anura Kumara Dissanayake, Udaya Kammanpila and Aturaliye Ratna Thera walked out of the meeting before its conclusion."
      ],
